the following bbcode will be installed on your site for local article links to work correctly
bbCode usage:
[kb]{INTTEXT},{TEXT}[/kb]
html replacement:
<a href="kb.php?a={INTTEXT}">{TEXT}</a>
helpline:
[kb]article id number, article name[/kb]

If you plan on using SEO you will need to change the html replacement to:
<a href="a{INTTEXT}.html" class="postlink kblink">{TEXT}</a>
